        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;“I &lt;em&gt;live&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;breathe&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;sleep&lt;/em&gt; Swift.” - Monte Thakkar&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am really passionate about iOS development and I find developing new iOS apps challenging yet fun. I am looking for internship/ full-time opportunities as a iOS Developer to work on ideas that are making (or plan to make) a difference&lt;/p&gt;

